Subject: [PATCH 15/48] trails: optional per-resort trail status plugin

Resorts opt in with "trails" in resort.json (true = same page as lifts,
or a {host, pathname} url object) plus a lib/resorts/<id>/trails.js parse
descriptor in the same idiom as lift parsers. Parsed rows carry an
optional difficulty level (green/blue/black/doubleBlack/terrainPark).
Served as data.trails = { stats, list } alongside lifts.
